OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLeicester widow petitions  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor progress on betting law
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Freview                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A widow has handed in a petition       
OL,6, calling on the government to publish a 
OL,7, review of gambling laws.               
OL,9,FAnnie Ashton, from Leicester, has      
OL,10,Fcalled for a review of the law since   
OL,11,Fher husband Luke killed himself.       
OL,13,FShe said he developed a gambling       
OL,14,Fdisorder while he was furloughed and   
OL,15,Fdespite his efforts to stop, the offer 
OL,16,Fof "free bets" kept luring him back.   
OL,18,FThe government said it was "determined 
OL,19,Fto protect those most at risk of       
OL,20,Fgambling-related harm".                
